\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces MVT-RAG pipeline for adaptive section switching in scientific RAG. Document sections are modeled as foraging patches; the algorithm estimates the environmental average return $G_{\mathrm  {env}}$ from a lightweight initial pass, then iteratively retrieves from the highest-potential section and switches when marginal gain falls below $G_{\mathrm  {env}}$.}}{2}{figure.1}\protected@file@percent }
